{
  "stem": "25639.11",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I made up my mind that I will never rest until I bring my family out of there to this free country.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when I came back, that is the first thing I attended to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was a period when nobody had any luck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was very persistent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I tried, and tried again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, and finally, I think they got tired of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They permitted my father to come for a visit after trying him to come on a permanent basis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And when he was here, as soon as he stepped off the plane, and we met, he said, I will never return.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "However, our doctor was able to help out, and, and he developed a heart problem.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He actually came here with it, which he didn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so, we were able to use that as the reason for him not returning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "For every year, he received a letter in Russian, when are you coming back, from the authorities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "After Dad came, we brought my sister over and her husband and three children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And following that, my brother, his wife, and three children, and then my other brother and his family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so it-- there were all sorts of complications.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they're all here in this wonderful land of freedom, really working very hard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they put their pennies together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They didn't even buy themselves a ticket to a theater, or a concert.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They wanted everybody who worked-- who had part time jobs and went to school-- to put their little bits of money together, so that they could have a down payment for a house.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And when that house was purchased, everybody's name went on the title.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My husband tried to advise them that this may not be the wisest thing to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
